      "title": "Train Operations resume after curfew",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); Sri Lanka Railways says that with the lifting of the curfew trains will operate as usual on Thursday (14).",
        "General Manager of Sri Lanka Railways Dhammika Jayasundara said that the train services resumed from 5.00 AM today (14).",
        "The Sri Lanka Transport Board (SLTB) says that buses will be operating today (14) as usual.",
        "However, the Lanka Private Bus Owners\u2019 Association said that the private bus servicea have been disrupted today (14)."
      ],
